{"tid":1876122,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曹世鎬、南昶熙一週偶像下車","createTime":"2020-02-12T08:06:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T06:35:25.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0dd4507aed3fdd685cd56857f046d31edb5bb902","tid":1876122,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:06:07.000Z","msg":"笑星曹世鎬和南昶熙《一週偶像》下車。<br />\n<br />\n12日OSEN的採訪結果顯示，曹世鎬、南昶熙最近退出了MBC 《一週偶像》的主持人一職。<br />\n<br />\n曹世鎬、南昶熙、光熙去年1月9日作為《一週偶像》的主持人與觀眾們打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n曹世鎬、南昶熙雖然退出了《一週偶像》,但是光熙依舊不變。 短期內《一週偶像》將延續光熙和特別MC的體制。 最近和Super Junior成員銀赫一起擔任了特別MC。<br />\n<br />\n2011年7月首播的《一週偶像》是一檔以復古風格挖掘偶像的節目。 以&quot;2倍速舞蹈&quot;,&quot;隨機舞蹈&quot;等環節流行而成爲話題,成為MBCevery1招牌綜藝節目。<br />\n<br />\n走左兩件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d305e709dd83eb8047efab6df6e4c45caeee55c","tid":1876122,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:08:10.000Z","msg":"趁愛豆房收左皮 週偶準備做翻大勢.."},{"pid":"1c41e815ab2996238373ad6781bde3283976f501","tid":1876122,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d305e709dd83eb8047efab6df6e4c45caeee55c","tid":1876122,"uid":46435,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:08:10.000Z","msg":"趁愛豆房收左皮 週偶準備做翻大勢.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:09:13.000Z","msg":"搵希澈老師做就得...光熙始終差D"},{"pid":"6781ce972cc83d910fa08415e458f002bd83cd1d","tid":1876122,"uid":3405,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"無dony cony根本不值一提"},{"pid":"96449a63a92bd8d84afb316d9921e46e4fd5a770","tid":1876122,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"光熙都幾厚面皮"},{"pid":"6e54603ff9384904367e4d35c1c4796ca00566b6","tid":1876122,"uid":115268,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"96449a63a92bd8d84afb316d9921e46e4fd5a7